        "cooked": "<p>I tried testing with public models and found that the issue doesn\u2019t seem to be related to model complexity, but rather that 3MF files with colors can\u2019t be exported. If I unify the colors, the export works. However, my model has complex coloring, and without automatic coloring it would be a lot of trouble, so I\u2019m not sure how to fix this.</p>",
